  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，倭奴国来贡，汉赐以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">汉倭奴国王</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">之印；二月，光武帝死，皇太子庄嗣位，是为汉明帝刘庄。是岁，全国有户四百二十七万零六百三十四，口两千一百万七千八百二十</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
