  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">汉和帝永元三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">91</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">窦宪大破北单于于金微山，北单于遁，其弟於除鞬自立为单于，款塞请降</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"><br>
  </span><span style="font-family:宋体">；十二月，复置西域都护</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
