  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">105</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">和帝死，少子隆以皇太子嗣位，是为汉殇帝，皇太后邓氏临朝称制</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
