  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">755</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十一月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">安史之乱爆发。十二月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">叛军陷洛阳。唐监军边令诚奉诏杀封常清、高仙芝于军中</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:30.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐玄宗天宝十五载</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">756</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">安禄山称帝于洛阳</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">国号燕。六月，叛军陷潼关。玄宗奔蜀，至马嵬兵变，杀杨贵妃。太子李亨走灵武。叛军陷长安。七月，李亨即位于灵武，是为肃宗</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"> </span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:30.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐肃宗至德二载</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">757</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，安禄山为其子安庆绪所杀。九月，唐军与回纥军克长安。十月，唐军克洛阳，安庆绪逃往邺郡。置左右神武军，至此北衙始有六军</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:21.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐肃宗乾元元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">758</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">以鱼朝恩为观军容使，总监郭子仪等九节度使大军数十万围安庆绪于相州</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">邺郡</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；置度支、盐铁、都团练使</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">废采访使，更置观察使</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:19.5pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐肃宗乾元二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">759</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">三月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">史思明增援安庆绪</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">败九节度使兵于邺城，旋杀庆绪，还范阳，四月，自称大燕皇帝，九月，攻占洛阳</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:11.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:11.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐肃宗上元二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:11.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">761</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:11.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">三月，史思明为其子史朝义所杀</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:30.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐肃宗宝应元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">762</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，玄宗、肃宗相继去世；宦官李辅国、程元振拥立太子李豫，是为唐代宗；八月，浙东袁晁起义</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:27.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:27.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐代宗广德元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:27.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">763</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:27.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，史朝义自缢，余党降唐，安史之乱结束；十月，吐蕃攻占长安十余日，代宗奔陕州；十二月，代宗返长安</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">神策军扈从</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">入为禁军</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:21.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐代宗大历元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">766</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:21.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">吐蕃取甘州、肃州，唐河西节度使徙治凉州；南诏王阁罗凤立《南诏德化碑》于太和城</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:11.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
