  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐德宗建中二十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">805</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:30.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，德宗去世，子李诵继立，是为顺宗。八月，宦官俱文珍、节度使韦皋等逼顺宗让位于太子纯，改元永贞，是为唐宪宗。永贞革新失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:29.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐宪宗元和二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">807</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李吉甫撰《元和国计簿》成，总计全国方镇四十八，州府二百九十五，县一千四百五十三，每岁国家财赋倚办止于东南八道四十四九州，一百十四万户，比天宝税户四分减三</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:39.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:39.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐宪宗元和三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:39.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">808</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:39.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">牛僧孺、李宗闵等应直言极谏科，指陈时政，宰相李吉甫恶之，贬主考官，抑牛僧孺等人，启牛李党争之端</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐宪宗元和八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">813</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李吉甫撰《元和郡县图志》成</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
