  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">魏博镇叛，河北三镇又恢复独立状态</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
