  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">901</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:15.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，昭宗复位，杀刘季述等。二月，封朱温为梁王。冬，宰相崔胤召朱温入关，谋诛宦官，宦官劫昭宗走凤翔，依李茂贞。朱温兵围凤翔</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:17.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:17.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐昭宗天复二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:17.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">902</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:17.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">封钱鏐为越王。封杨行密为吴王；南诏权臣郑买嗣杀其王舜化真，建大长和国，蒙氏所建的南诏灭亡</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:5.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:5.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐昭宗天复三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:5.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">903</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:5.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李茂贞势蹙，被迫送昭宗出凤翔。朱温拥昭宗还京</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">废神策军中尉，以朝臣为枢密使。唐封王建为蜀王</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐昭宗天复四年</span></p>
