  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">904</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，朱温逼迁昭宗于洛阳。八月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">朱温遣人杀昭宗</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">立其子李柷，是为哀帝</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:14.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:14.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">唐哀帝天祐二年</span></p>
