  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:14.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">905</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:14.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">以刘隐为清海军节度使；朱温贬杀朝臣，史称</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">白马驿之祸</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；杨行密卒，子杨渥立，军政大权旁落大将徐温、张颢之手</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:39.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
