  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:39.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">907</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:39.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，朱温逼哀帝禅让，自即帝位，改名朱晃，是为后梁太祖朱晃，改国号为梁</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">史称后梁</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">都开封；<a href="http://www.lishi.net/html/tangchao/" target="_blank">唐朝</a>亡；后梁封马殷为楚王；钱鏐为吴越王；任高季兴为荆南节度使；王建称帝，国号蜀，史称前蜀</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后梁开平三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
