  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，朱温第三子友贞发动政变，友珪自杀，友贞即位，是为末帝。复都开封</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.0pt">
