  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">契丹首领耶律阿保机称帝，是为辽太祖耶律亿，建契丹国</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:14.25pt">
