  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，辽太祖定法律，正班爵</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:14.25pt">
