  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:8.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后唐同光三年</span></p>
