  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后唐令国子监依西京石经本校定九经，雕版印制。官府大规模刻书自此始</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:8.25pt">
