  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">夏，河东节度使石敬瑭上表，以幽蓟十六州为代价，换取契丹援助。九月，契丹军南下，大败后唐军。十一月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">辽太宗册封石敬瑭为帝，国号晋，史称后晋。闰十一月，石敬瑭攻入洛阳，末帝从珂自杀，后唐亡</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
