  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">徐知诰改名李昇，改国号为唐，史称南唐；辽太宗诏以皇都为上京，升幽州为南京，南京为东京</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
