  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后晋高祖石敬瑭卒，侄石重贵继位，史称出帝或少帝</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:14.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
