  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，元仁宗死。三月，太子硕德八剌嗣帝位，是为元英宗硕德八剌</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:35.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:35.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元英宗至治三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:35.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1323</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:35.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，《大元通制》成，颁行天下；八月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">硕德八剌自上都还</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">驻南坡，为铁失等所杀。九月，晋王也孙铁木儿即帝位，是为泰定帝</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:40.5pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:40.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元文宗天历元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:40.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1328</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:40.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，泰定帝死。九月，泰定皇太子阿速吉八即帝位于上都。燕铁木儿于大都发动政变，迎元武宗之子图帖睦尔为帝，是为元文宗。十月，上都政权失败。十一月，图帖睦尔遣使往漠北迎其兄和世</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Mojikyo M104&quot;">歛</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:29.25pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元文宗天历二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1329</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:29.25pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，和世</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Mojikyo M104&quot;">歛</span><span style="font-family:宋体">于和林北即帝位，是为明宗。八月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">和世</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Mojikyo M104&quot;">歛</span><span style="font-family:宋体">南来</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">与图帖睦尔相会于王忽察都，数日后暴死。图帖睦尔复即帝位</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:19.5pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元文宗至顺三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1332</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:19.5pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">八月，元文宗死。十月，明宗和世</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Mojikyo M104&quot;">歛</span><span style="font-family:宋体">次子懿璘质班被立为帝，十一月死，庙号宁宗</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝元统元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1333</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">六月，和世</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Mojikyo M104&quot;">歛</span><span style="font-family:宋体">长子妥欢帖睦尔即帝位，是为元顺帝妥欢贴睦尔</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1342</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，教皇伯涅的克十二世使节来中国，抵达上都</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1344</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，黄河决口，山东、河北皆受灾</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:21.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1345</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十月，《辽史》、《金史》、《宋史》修成；十一月，《至正条格》成</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:9.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:9.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1348</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:9.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">台州方国珍起事，聚众海上</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1351</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，修治黄河。十一月，黄河堤成；五月，颍州刘福通起义。八月，蕲州徐寿辉起义，国号天完。</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1352</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，濠州郭子兴、孙德崖等起义。闰三月，朱元璋投奔郭子兴。八月，徐州被元军攻陷，李二死。是年，天完红巾军攻克长江中下游广大地区</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1353</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，淮东张士诚起义，攻克高邮等地。是年，元军大举反攻，天完红巾军连遭挫折</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1354</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，张士诚称诚王，国号大周。九月，元丞相脱脱率大军围高邮。元顺帝突然下令罢脱脱官爵，元军溃散</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1355</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，刘福通迎韩山童之子韩林儿为帝</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">建国号宋</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">改元龙凤。韩林儿号小明王。是年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">天完红巾军复起</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">连败元军</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1356</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，张士诚部渡江攻克平江等地。三月，朱元璋取集庆。是年，天完、宋红巾军分头出击，连获胜利</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">元顺帝至正十七年</span></p>
