  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">冬，俺答孙把汉那吉降明；应天巡抚海瑞疏浚吴淞江，浚白茆河</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">并抑制豪强</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">被劾离职</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:21.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明穆宗隆庆五年</span></p>
