  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:21.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，穆宗死。六月，太子翊钧即位，是为明神宗；张居正任首辅</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.75pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.75pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历元年</span></p>
