  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">爱新觉罗</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">·</span><span style="font-family:宋体">努尔哈赤袭封为指挥使，起兵攻尼堪外兰</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1587</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明政府封索南嘉措为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">朵只儿唱达赖喇嘛</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；海瑞死于南京右都御史任，人民为之罢市致哀</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1588</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">努尔哈赤统一建州五部</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1590</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">以大理评事雒于仁谏疏，神宗不欲外人得知，留中不发，自是章奏留中遂成为例</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1592</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，日本关白丰臣秀吉侵朝鲜。明兵赴援，大败。乃任李如松为防海御倭总兵官</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1593</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李如松收复平壤、开城，进攻王京，日军弃王京，退据釜山。明撤主力回国</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:12.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1594</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:12.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">吏部郎中顾宪成被责革职，遂回无锡修东林书院，讽议朝政评论人物，东林党议始于此</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
