  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">遣宦官赴通州、天津征税</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">从此税使继矿使四出</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
