  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1597</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">日本再侵朝鲜</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1598</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明军再次赴援。丰臣秀吉死，日军撤走</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1599</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">遣宦官至各地征税、办矿。临清、沙市、武昌等地民变</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历二十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1600</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">播州杨应龙作乱多年，明军平乱，史称播州之役；耶稣会教士利玛窦到京，神宗允许在京师建教堂传教</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历三十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1604</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">发生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">楚宗之乱</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。宗室数百人大肆抢掠</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历四十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1615</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">梃击案发，杀张差结案；努尔哈赤正式建立八旗制度</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历四十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1616</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，努尔哈赤在赫图阿拉称汗，国号金，史称后金</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历四十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1618</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后金汗努尔哈赤以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">七大恨</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">誓师征明</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">毁抚顺</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">拔清河堡</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:6.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明神宗万历四十七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1619</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:6.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明经略杨镐率四路军攻后金，大败。萨尔浒之战，西路军被歼；后金灭叶赫海西女真扈伦四部均亡</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明光宗泰昌元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1620</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，神宗死。八月，太子常洛即位，是为光宗。光宗病，红丸案发。廷臣恐光宗选侍李氏操纵朝政</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">迫令迁宫</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">是为移宫案。皇长子由校即位，是为熹宗</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1621</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后金攻陷沈阳</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">又陷辽阳。后金迁都辽阳</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1622</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">荷兰人入侵台湾；白莲教首领徐鸿儒在山东起义，称中兴福烈帝，不久败死</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1623</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">阉党顾秉谦、魏广微入阁。魏忠贤提督东厂</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1625</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">魏忠贤兴大狱，捕杀杨涟、左光斗、魏大中等人</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">杀前辽东经略熊廷弼，罢孙承宗，命放弃关外各城；三月，后金迁都沈阳，是为盛京</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1626</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">苏州居民因反对滥捕东林党人，发生民变。后颜佩韦、杨念如等五人挺身投案被杀，葬于虎丘，称五人墓；八月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">努尔哈赤死。九月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">皇太极即位，是为清太宗</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">；后金制订</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"> “</span><span style="font-family:宋体">逃人法</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明熹宗天启七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1627</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">皇太极攻宁远、锦州，被袁崇焕击退，时称宁锦大捷；八月，熹宗死，弟信王由检即位，是为明思宗。十一月，宣布魏忠贤罪状，魏自缢死</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1628</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">以袁崇焕为兵部尚书，总督蓟辽；陕西连旱，王嘉胤、高迎祥等起义，明末农民战争开始；张溥、孙淳等联合几社、闻社、南社、匡社等结成复社</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1629</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">后金大举攻明，袁崇焕入援；崇祯帝中后金反间计，将袁下狱；开历局，以徐光启监督</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1630</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李自成参加起义；张献忠起义于陕西米脂</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1635</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">高迎祥、张献忠东进，破凤阳。明廷因战区扩大，命卢象升总督山、陕；张献忠率部西入陕西，与李自成合</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1636</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">高迎祥为孙传庭所杀，李自成代为闯王；四月，皇太极即帝位，改国号为清</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1637</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">宋应星所著《天工开物》刊行</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1638</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明廷推行招抚政策，张献忠据谷城受抚，但拒绝解甲。李自成屡为明军所败，兵力微弱，起义军入商雒山中；清多尔衮大举攻明；清改蒙古衙门为理藩院</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1639</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">张献忠谷城再起</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">破房山、保康。九月，杨嗣昌出京督师</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1640</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">张献忠、罗汝才合兵攻四川，破绵州，逼成都。李自成重入河南</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1641</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">张献忠东进。正月，破明军于川东开县黄陵城。二月，破襄阳</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">进破光州等地。李自成攻入洛阳，杀明福王朱常洵</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1642</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清军攻陷松山　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"> </span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1643</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李自成自称</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">奉天倡义文武大元帅</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；八月，清太宗死，子福临即位，是为清世祖。以郑亲王济尔哈朗、亲王多尔衮辅政；九月，李自成进兵汝州，大败孙传庭。十月，破潼关</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">明思宗崇祯十七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1644</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，李自成陷西安，改西安为长安，号西京，于西安称王，国号</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体">大顺</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；三月，李自成率大顺军攻占北京</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">明崇祯帝自缢</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">明亡</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体;text-transform:uppercase">清世祖顺治元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana;text-transform:uppercase">1644</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体;
  text-transform:uppercase">四月，山海关之战，李自成败退，吴三桂引清军入关。五月，多尔衮率清军入北京。明福王朱由崧在南京即帝位，建立南明弘光政权。九月，福临</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana;text-transform:uppercase">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体;text-transform:uppercase">顺治帝</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana;text-transform:uppercase">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体;text-transform:uppercase">入北京，十月，即帝位。以多尔衮为叔父摄政王。遣豫亲王多铎西进潼关，英亲王阿济格由边外进，西击李自成军。十二月，颁圈地令</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana;text-transform:uppercase">&nbsp;</span></p>
