  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">台湾爆发天地会领袖林爽文领导的汉族、高山族农民起义，两年后失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清高宗乾隆五十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1788</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">八月，廓尔喀入侵后藏</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清高宗乾隆五十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1791</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">廓尔喀再次入侵，进犯日喀则，洗劫扎什伦布寺；十一月，派福康安调兵入藏迎击</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清高宗乾隆五十七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1792</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">乾隆帝定金瓶掣签决定达赖、班禅转世灵童之制</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清高宗乾隆五十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1793</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">颁布《钦定西藏章程》。六月，英国马戛尔尼使团到达大沽；八月，乾隆帝在热河行宫接见英国使节</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清高宗乾隆六十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1795</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">九月，立皇十五子颙琰为皇太子</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">定明年继承皇位</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">改元嘉庆</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清仁宗嘉庆元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1796</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，举行授受大典，颙琰即位，尊弘历为太上皇帝；川、楚、陕、甘、豫五省白莲教起义爆发，九年后失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清仁宗嘉庆四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1799</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正月，弘历卒，颙琰亲政；处死大学士和珅，籍没家产</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清仁宗嘉庆十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1813</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">九月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">天理教起义。林清率领的起义军攻入紫禁城，旋败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清仁宗嘉庆二十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1820</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">颙琰卒</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">旻宁继位，改元道光；大和卓之孙张格尔在浩罕封建统治者与英国殖民者支持下，潜入南疆发动叛乱</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1821</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清廷重申禁烟令，严禁在澳门、黄埔囤放和售卖鸦片</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1827</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">张格尔叛乱被平定</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1838</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十一月，命林则徐为钦差大臣，前往广州办理禁烟事宜</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光十九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1839</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月二十二（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">3</span><span style="font-family:
   宋体">日</span><span style="font-family:宋体">），林则徐在虎门海滩销毁收缴的鸦片</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1840</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清廷命琦善为钦差大臣，赴广州与英谈判。林则徐被革职。十二月（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1841</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"> 1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月），英军攻陷虎门外沙角、大角炮台，鸦片战争爆发</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1841</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">一月，清廷下诏宣战。二月，英军攻陷虎门炮台。四月，英军攻击广州城，奕山向英军乞和，签订《广州和约》，七月以后，英舰队北犯，攻陷厦门、镇海、宁波</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1842</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">英军攻陷吴淞炮台</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">英国舰队进入长江</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">六月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">攻陷镇江，七月，进抵南京江面，七月二十四（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">8 </span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">29</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日）清廷被迫签订《江宁条约》</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">《南京条约》</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；十二月，魏源著《海国图志》五十卷</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1843</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">八月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">中英在虎门签订《五口通商附粘善后条款》（《虎门条约》）</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1844</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">先后签订中美《望厦条约》、中法《黄埔条约》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1845</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十一月，英国驻沪领事与上海道台订立《上海租地章程》，是为外国侵略者在中国设立租界之始</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光二十九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1849</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">一月，英国香港总督文翰带兵强入广州城，广州社学率众十万余人反对，文翰被迫放弃入城要求</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣宗道光三十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1850</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">一月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">旻宁卒</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">奕詝继位，改元咸丰；十二月初十</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(1851<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:宋体"><span lang="EN-US">年</span></span>1<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:宋体"><span lang="EN-US">月</span></span>11<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:宋体"><span lang="EN-US">日</span></span>)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">太平天国金田起义开始</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1851</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">闰八月，太平军克永安；十月，封王建制　</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1852</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">太平军自永安突围</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">大败清军向荣、乌兰泰部</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，破全州；十一月占汉阳、汉口；十二月攻克武昌。清廷命在籍礼部侍郎曾国藩帮办湖南团练；捻军张乐行在安徽蒙城雉河集起义</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1853</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">太平军沿长江东下</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">占领南京，定为首都，改称天京</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">四月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">派林凤祥、李开芳率军北伐，同时，派胡以晃、赖汉英率军溯江西征。清军在天京城东孝陵卫建立江南大营，在扬州建立江北大营，包围天京；八月，上海小刀会首领刘丽川起义，两年后失败；冬，太平天国颁布《天朝田亩制度》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1854</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十二月，太平军在江西湖口大败湘军水师</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1855</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">太平军北伐失败，主将林凤祥、李开芳牺牲；各路捻军会集雉河集，推张乐行为盟主；贵州苗民起义，十七年后失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1856</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，太平军大败江北营统帅托明阿部，五月，攻破江南大营，向荣自杀，八月，天京事变，韦昌辉诛杀东王杨秀清，十月被处死。石达开回天京提理政务；云南回民起义</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">攻占大理</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">建立政权，十六年后失败；英国借口亚罗号事件，挑起第二次鸦片战争</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1857</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，石达开受洪秀全猜忌，率十万众自天京出走；十一月，英法联军占领广州</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1858</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，英法联军攻陷大沽炮台；沙俄东西伯利亚总督穆拉维约夫胁迫清黑龙江将军奕山签订《瑷珲条约》；五月，俄、美、英、法逼迫清廷相继签订《天津条约》；八月，陈玉成等再破清军江北大营</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1859</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，科尔沁亲王僧格林沁在大沽挫败来犯的英法舰队；冬，太平天国颁布洪仁玕所著《资政新篇》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1860</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">三月，太平军再破江南大营，并东占苏、常，建苏福省；美国人华尔组成</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">洋枪队</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，协助清廷镇压太平军；六月，英法联军占领天津；八月，英法联军攻陷北京，抢掠、焚毁圆明园；九月，恭亲王奕訢与英、法、俄分别签订《北京条约》；十二月，清廷设立总理各国事务衙门</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清文宗咸丰十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1861</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，奕詝卒，九月，慈禧发动政变，逮捕载垣、端华、肃顺等赞襄王大臣。载淳即皇帝位</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">改元同治。慈禧、慈安两太后垂帘听政，史称辛酉政变；曾国藩创办安庆内军械所，后李鸿章在上海设立江南制造总局，清代洋务运动自此始</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1862</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">正式设立同文馆。曾国荃督湘军进逼天京，扎营雨花台；左宗棠部湘军援浙江，李鸿章部淮军援上海，图苏、常，天京腹背受敌；陕甘回民起义</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1863</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，石达开在四川大渡河紫打地兵败自投清营，被杀</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1864</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，洪秀全病逝，幼主洪天贵福即位。六月，天京为清军攻陷，洪天贵福突围后在江西南昌遇害。太平天国起义失败。捻军和太平军遵王赖文光部联合，举赖文光为领袖</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1865</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">捻军在山东菏泽高楼寨击僧格林沁，歼全军七千余人。清廷急调曾国藩为钦差大臣，督湘淮军攻捻；中亚浩罕汗国军事头目阿古柏侵入新疆</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1866</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李鸿章接曾国藩任钦差大臣，督师</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">剿捻</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。捻军分为东西二部。　　左宗棠在福建马尾设立福州船政局；后调任陕甘总督，镇压西捻军和西北回民起义</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1867</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">阿古柏在新疆建立所谓</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">哲德沙尔汗国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">政权，自立为汗</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1868</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">六月，蒲安臣在华盛顿代表清政府与美国订《蒲安臣条约》；东西捻军相继覆没</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1870</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，天津教案发生。直隶、江西、福建、广东、四川等省相继爆发反洋教斗争；阿古柏攻占乌鲁木齐，天山南北路部分地区为其占据</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1871</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">沙俄出兵强占新疆伊犁地区</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1872</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">李鸿章在上海创办轮船招商局，侨商陈启源在广东南海县创办继昌隆缫丝局，中国民族资本主义近代工业开始出现；容闳等奉命率一批幼童三十名到美国留学，是为近代第一批留学生</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1873</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">左宗棠出兵河西走廊，占领肃州，陕甘回民起义失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清穆宗同治十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1874</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十二月，载淳卒，载湉继位，是为清德宗，改元光绪。慈禧太后再度垂帘听政</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1875</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">英国入侵云南，发生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">马嘉理事件</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；七月，清廷以兵部侍郎郭嵩焘任出使英国钦差大臣，为中国正式派遣驻外使节的开始</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1876</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">左宗棠讨伐阿古柏，收复乌鲁木齐，天山北部平定；英国以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">马嘉理事件</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">为借口，迫使清政府与之订立《烟台条约》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1877</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">春，清军进入南疆，阿古柏在库尔勒服毒死，清军收复除沙俄侵占的伊犁地区以外的全部新疆国土；李鸿章、唐廷枢筹建开平矿务局</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1880</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">左宗棠创办的兰州机器织呢局开工投产；李鸿章奏办天津北洋水师学堂、南北洋电报</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1883</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">中法战争爆发。法军占领河内、南定，越南国王请刘永福所部黑旗军助越抗法。四月，两军在河内城西的纸桥激战，大败法军，击毙法军司令李维业中校</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1884</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">五月，法国派遣远东舰队司令孤拔率舰队侵入福建马尾，福州水师覆没。七月，清廷下诏对法宣战。法国舰队占领台湾基隆炮台，封锁台湾海峡；新疆改建行省</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1885</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">镇南关大捷。四月，李鸿章和法国公使巴德诺在天津签订《中法会订越南条约》</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">即《中法新约》</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。中法战争结束；台湾改建行省</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1886</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">英军由锡金侵入西藏</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1888</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">北洋海军建成，以丁汝昌为提督，林泰曾、刘步蟾为左右翼总兵，拥有舰船二十五艘，四万余吨</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1889</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">二月，光绪帝载湉亲政；十一月，李鸿章创办的上海机器织布局投产</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1890</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">张之洞在汉阳兴建铁厂</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1894</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">中日甲午战争爆发。七月初一</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(8.1)</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">中日两国同时宣战。八月十六，日军进攻朝鲜平壤，清军败绩，总兵左宝贵壮烈牺牲。两日后，北洋海军与日舰队在黄海激战，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">致远</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">舰管带邓世昌殉国。九月，日军渡鸭绿江攻入中国境内。十月，占大连、旅顺。十二月，日军在山东半岛荣成湾龙须岛登陆。孙中山在檀香山创立兴中会，提出</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">驱逐鞑虏，恢复中华，创立合众政府</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的革命纲领</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1895</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">一月，日军攻占威海卫，北洋海军覆没，丁汝昌、刘步蟾自杀殉国。三月二十三日李鸿章与日本政府签订《马关条约》，把辽东半岛和台湾全岛及所有附属各岛屿</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(</span><span style="font-family:宋体">包括澎湖列岛</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">割让给日本。俄、德、法三国照会日本，劝告放弃辽东半岛，日本被迫接受，清政府以银三千万两赎回，史称三国干涉还辽；康有为联合十八省会试举人一千三百余人</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">公车上书</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">" </span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1896</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，李鸿章与沙俄代表签订《中俄密约》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1897</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">德国武装占领胶州湾；沙俄出兵强占旅大</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1898</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">四月，与英国签订关于香港对岸九龙半岛以九十九年为期的租借条约；四月二十三日</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">光绪帝下</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">明定国是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">诏书</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">戊戌变法开始。八月初六</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">(9 </span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">21</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">)</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，慈禧幽禁光绪帝于瀛台，重新</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">临朝训政</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">；康有为、梁启超逃亡日本，谭嗣同等六君子遇害。百日维新失败；山东冠县义和拳首举义旗</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十五年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1899</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">山东义和团朱红灯部在平原县起义；八月，美国国务卿海约翰先后照会英、俄、日、意、法、德诸国，提出在中国实行</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"><br>
  "</span><span style="font-family:宋体">门户开放</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">政策。张謇筹办的南通大生纱厂建成投产</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十六年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1900</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">义和团进入京津地区。驻京各国公使以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">保护使馆</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">为名调集军队四百余人到达北京。各国海军舰艇开到大沽口。由英国海军上将西摩尔统率的八国联军进犯北京，遭义和团和爱国清军阻击败回天津。义和团猛攻北京东交民巷使馆区和西什库教堂。五月二十五日，清廷发出宣战诏书。八国联军占领大沽炮台后攻陷天津，七月二十，北京陷落。慈禧挟光绪帝仓惶逃走。沙俄制造海兰泡与江东六十四屯惨案，并派侵略军十余万人大举入侵东北。十二月，慈禧在西安下诏宣布</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">变法</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十七年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1901</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，以庆亲王奕劻、李鸿章为全权大臣，与俄、英、美、日、德、法、意、奥、比、西、荷十一国公使签订《辛丑条约》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十八年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1902</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">英国再次入侵西藏。一月，梁启超在日本横滨创办《新民丛报》，鼓吹保皇。三月，中俄签订《交收东三省条约》</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪二十九年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1903</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">闰五月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">《苏报》案发生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">章炳麟、邹容被捕系于租界西牢</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana"><br>
  </span><span style="font-family:宋体">十二月，日俄战争爆发，清政府宣布严守</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">局外中立</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">；黄兴、宋教仁等组织革命团体华兴会于长沙</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三十年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1904</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">英军攻陷拉萨，达赖十三世出走青海；蔡元培、陶成章等在上海组织革命团体光复会</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三十一年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1905</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">废除科举考试制度；发生抵制美货运动；同盟会在东京召开成立大会，通过会章，选举孙中山为总理，机关报《民报》创刊；吴樾在前门车站炸出洋考察宪政的载泽等五大臣，炸伤载泽、绍英，吴樾死难。</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三十二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1906</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">七月，清廷发布谕旨，宣布</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:
  宋体">预备仿行宪政</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">（预备立宪）。张謇、郑孝胥、汤寿潜等在上海组织</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span><span style="font-family:宋体">预备立宪公会</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">"</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三十三年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1907</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">八月，清廷发布上谕，设立资政院；九月，令各省设咨议局；同盟会发动一系列起义，均遭失败。徐锡麟在安庆刺杀安徽巡抚恩铭，发动起义</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体">事败牺牲。秋瑾在绍兴准备响应徐锡麟起义，事泄，英勇就义</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清德宗光绪三十四年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1908</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清廷宣布预备立宪以九年为期，颁布《钦定宪法大纲》；十月二十一日，载湉卒，溥仪继位，改元宣统，由摄政王载沣监国。次日，慈禧卒</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣统元年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1909</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">十六省咨议局相继成立，派代表到北京请愿，请速开国会</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣统二年</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;
  height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:Verdana">1910</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width="70%" style="width:70.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:double black 2.25pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">发生国会请愿运动。清廷宣布将原定九年的预备立宪期缩短为三年。资政院开幕；光复会在东京成立总部，推章炳麟、陶成章为正副会长；广州新军起义失败</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr style="height:3.0pt">
  <td width="15%" style="width:15.0%;border-top:none;border-left:double black 2.25pt;
  border-bottom:double black 2.25pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:
  .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:3.0pt">
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt"><span style="font-family:宋体">清宣统三年</span></p>
